{"id":1475250825,"question_id":3,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"1 week, 2 days","timestamp":1733836023,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"17 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1475250825/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"14.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int left=0, right=0;\n        int maxlen = 0;\n        unordered_set<char> st;\n        while(right < s.length()) {\n            while(st.find(s[right]) != st.end()) {\n                st.erase(s[left]);\n                left++;\n            }\n            st.insert(s[right]);\n            maxlen = max(maxlen, right - left + 1);\n            right++;\n        }\n        return maxlen;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
